00:01:00.730 --> 00:01:07.520
and bringing the the leg toward the midline,
or the median plane, of the body. Now the

00:01:07.520 --> 00:01:13.250
first one we have shown there is in green
and is called adductor magnus. Adductor means

00:01:13.250 --> 00:01:17.781
it's an adductor muscle, of course, and magnus
is the Latin word for great or large and you

00:01:17.781 --> 00:01:22.290
can see it's a very large muscle. We can't
